quran[564]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,Yeh log kis cheez ke baarey mei puch-gajj kar rahe hain
  78,2,Kya us badi khabar ke baarey mein
  78,3,Jiske mutaaliq yeh mukhtalif che-mei-goiyan (disagreement) karne mein lagey huey hain
  78,4,Hargiz nahin an-qareeb inhein maloom ho jayega
  78,5,"Haan hargiz nahin, an-qareeb inhein maloom ho jayega"
  78,6,Kya yeh waqiya nahin hai ke humne zameen ko farsh banaya
  78,7,Aur pahadon ko mekhon(pegs) ki tarah gaad diya
  78,8,Aur tumhein (mardon aur auraton ke) jodon ki shakal mein paida kiya
  78,9,Aur tumhari neend ko baaisey sukoon banaya
  78,10,Aur raat ko purdah posh
  78,11,Aur din ko muaash ka waqt banaya
  78,12,Aur Tumharey upar saat mazboot aasman qayam kiye
  78,13,Aur ek nihayat roshan aur garm chirag paida kya
  78,14,Aur baadalon se lagatar baarish barsayi
  78,15,Taa-ke iske zariye se galla(grain) aur sabzi
  78,16,Aur ghaney baagh ugaye
  78,17,Beshak faisley ka din ek mukarrar waqt hai
  78,18,Jis roz soor mei phook maar di jayegi tum fauj dar fauj nikal aaogey
  78,19,Aur aasmaan khol diya jayega hatta ke woh darwaze hi darwaze ban kar reh jayega
  78,20,Aur pahad chalaye jayenge yahan tak ke woh saraab(mirage) ho jayenge
  78,21,Dar haqeeqat jahannum ek ghaat(ambush) hai
  78,22,Sarkashon ka thikana
  78,23,Jismein woh muddaton padey rahengey
  78,24,Uske andar kisi thandak aur peene ke qabil kisi cheez ka maza woh na chakhengey
  78,25,kuch milega to bas garam paani aur zakhmon ka dho-wan(peep)
  78,26,(Unke kartuton) ka bharpur badla
  78,27,Woh kisi hisab ki tawakku na rakhte thay
  78,28,Aur hamari aayat ko unhon ne bilkul jhutla diya tha
  78,29,Aur haal yeh tha ke humne har cheez gin gin kar likh rakkhi thi
  78,30,"Ab chakho maza, Hum tumhare liye azaab ke siwa kisi cheez mei hargiz izafa na karengey"
  78,31,Yakeenan muttakiyon(pious) ke liye kamrani ka ek Muqaam hai
  78,32,Baagh aur angur
  78,33,Aur naukhez humsin ladkiyan
  78,34,Aur jhalakte huey jaam
  78,35,Wahan koi lagv(vain) aur jhuthi baat woh na sunengey
  78,36,Jazaa aur kafi inaam tumharey Rubb ki taraf se
  78,37,Us nihayat meharban khuda ki taraf se jo zameen aur aasmaano ka aur inke darmiyan ki har cheez ka malik hai jiske samney kisi ko bolne ka yara nahin
  78,38,Jis roz rooh aur malaika saff basta khade hongey. Koi na bolega siwaye uske jisey Rehman ijazat de aur jo theek baat kahey
  78,39,"Woh din bar-haqq hai, ab jiska jee chahey apne Rubb ki taraf palatne ka rasta ikhtiyar karle"
  78,40,"Humne tum logon ko us azaab se dara diya hai jo qareeb aa laga hai. Jis roz aadmi woh sab kuch dekh lega jo uske hathon ne aagey bheja hai, aur kafir pukar uthega ke kaash mai khaaq(mitti) hota"
  79,1,Kasam hai un (Farishton) ki jo doob kar khinchte hain
  79,2,aur aahistagi se (gently) nikaal le jataey hain
  79,3,Aur (un farishton ki jo qayinaat mein) tezi se tairtey phirtay hain
  79,4,phir (hukum baja laane mein) sabqat karte hain
  79,5,phir (ehkam-ilahi ke mutabiq) maamlaat ka intizam chalate hain
  79,6,Jis roz hila marey ga zalzalay ka jhatka
  79,7,Aur uske pichey ek aur jhatka padega
  79,8,Kuch dil hongey jo us roz khauf se kaanp rahey hongey
  79,9,Nigahein unki sehmi(downcast) hui hogi
  79,10,Yeh log kehte hain “Kya waqai hum palta kar phir wapas laaye jayenge?”
  79,11,“Kya jab hum khokli boseeda (hollow and rotten) haddiyan ban chuke hongey?”
  79,12,Kehne lagey “yeh wapsi to phir badey ghatey(nuksan) ki hogi”
  79,13,Halaanke yeh bas itna kaam hai ke ek zoar ki daant padegi
  79,14,Aur yakayk yeh khule maidan mein maujood hongey
  79,15,Kya tumhein Moosa ke qissey ki khabar pahunchi hai
  79,16,Jab uske Rubb ne usey Tuwa ke muqaddas wadi(valley) mein pukara tha
  79,17,"Ke Firaun ke paas ja, woh sarkash ho gaya hai"
  79,18,"Aur ussey keh, kya tu iske liye tayyar hai ke pakeezgi ikhtiyar karey"
  79,19,Aur mai terey Rubb ki taraf teri rehnumai karoon to (uska) khauf terey andar paida ho?”
  79,20,Phir Moosa ne (Firaun ke paas ja kar) usko badi nishani dikhai
  79,21,Magar usne jhutla diya aur na mana
  79,22,Phir chaal baaziyan karne ke liye palta
  79,23,Aur logon ko jama karke usne pukaar kar kaha
  79,24,“Main tumhara sabse bada Rubb hoon”
  79,25,Aakhir-e-kaar Allah ne usey aakhirat aur duniya ke azaab mei pakad liya
  79,26,Dar haqeeqat is mein badi ibrat hai har us shaks ke liye jo darey
  79,27,Kya tum logon ki takhleeq(paidaish) zyada sakht kaam hai ya aasmaan ki? Allah ne usko banaya
  79,28,Uski chhat(ceiling) khoob unchi uthayi phir uska tawazun qayam kiya(proportioned it)
  79,29,Aur uski raat dhaanki aur uska din nikala
  79,30,Iske baad zameen ko usne bichaya
  79,31,Uske andar se uska paani aur chara nikala
  79,32,Aur pahad usmein gaadh diye
  79,33,Saaman-e-zeist(provision) ke taur par tumharay liye aur tumharey maweshion ke liye
  79,34,Phir jab woh hungama-e-azeem barpa hoga
  79,35,Jis roz Insan apna sab kiya dhara yaad karega
  79,36,Aur har dekhne wale ke samney dozak khol kar rakh di jayegi
  79,37,To jisne sarkashi(transgress) ki thi
  79,38,Aur dunya ki zindagi ko tarjeeh di thi
  79,39,dozakh hi uska thikana hogi
  79,40,Aur jisne apne Rubb ke samney khade honay ka khauf kiya tha aur nafs ko buri khwaishaat se baaz rakha tha
  79,41,Jannat uska thikana hogi
  79,42,Yeh log tumse puchte hain ke aakhir woh ghadi kab aakar thehre gi
  79,43,Tumhara kya kaam ke us ka waqt batao
  79,44,Us ka ilm to Allah par khatm hai
  79,45,Tum sirf khabardar karne waley ho har us shaks ko jo uska khauff karey
  79,46,Jis roz yeh log usey dekh lengey to inhein yun mehsoos hoga ke (yeh duniya mein ya halat-e-mout mei) bas ek din ke pichle pehar ya aglay pehar tak thehrey hai
  80,1,"[The prophet] Tursh-rooh (frowned) hua aur berukhi barti"
  80,2,Is baat par ke woh andha us ke paas aa gaya
  80,3,"Tumhe kya khabar, shayad woh sudhar jaye"
  80,4,ya naseehat par dhyaan de aur naseeat karna us ke liye nafea(faiydamand) ho
  80,5,Jo shaks be-parwahi baratta hai
  80,6,Uski taraf to tum tawajjuh karte ho
  80,7,Halaanke agar wo na sudhrey to tum par uski kya zimmedari hai
  80,8,Aur jo khud tumharey paas dauda aata hai
  80,9,Aur woh darr raha hota hai
  80,10,Usse tum berukhi barat-tey ho
  80,11,Hargiz nahin yeh to ek naseehat hai
  80,12,jiska jee chahey isey qabool karey
  80,13,Yeh aisey saheefon mein darj hai jo mukarram hain
  80,14,"Buland martaba hain, pakeeza hain"
  80,15,muazzaz aur neik kaatibon ke
  80,16,haathon mein rehete hain
  80,17,Laanat ho Insan par kaisa sakht munkir-e-haq (denies the Truth) hai yeh
  80,18,Kis cheez se Allah ne isey paida kiya hai
  80,19,Nutfa ki ek boondh se Allah ne isey paida kiya phir iski taqdeer muqarrar ki
  80,20,Phir iske liye zindagi ki raah aasan ki
  80,21,Phir isey maut di aur qabr mei pahunchaya
  80,22,Phir jab chahey woh isey dobara utha khada karey
  80,23,"Hargiz nahi, isney woh farz ada nahi kiya jiska Allah ne isey hukum diya tha"
  80,24,Phir zara insaan apni khuraak(khane/food) ko dekhe
  80,25,Humne khoob paani lundhaya(poured)
  80,26,Phir zameen ko ajeeb tarah phada
  80,27,phir us ke andar ugaye galley(grain)
  80,28,Aur angoor aur tarkariyan
  80,29,Aur zaitoon aur khajoorein
  80,30,Aur ghaney baagh(orchards)
  80,31,Aur tarah tarah ke phal aur chaarey
  80,32,Tumharey liye aur tumharey maweshion(cattles) ke liye saman-e-zeist(provision )ke taur par
  80,33,Aakhir-e-kaar jab woh kaan behrey kar deney wali aawaz buland hogi
  80,34,Us roz aadmi apne bhai
  80,35,Aur apni maa aur apne baap
  80,36,Aur apni biwi aur apni aulad se bhagega
  80,37,Unmein har shaks par us din aisa waqt aa padega ke usay apne siwa kisi ka hosh na hoga
  80,38,Kuch chehrey us roz damak rahe hongey
  80,39,Hashash bashash aur khush o khurram hongey
  80,40,Aur kuch chehron par uss roz khaak(dust) udd rahi hogi
  80,41,Aur kalons(darkness) chayi hui hogi
  80,42,Yahi kafir o fajir (unbelivers and wicked) log hain
  81,1,Jab Suraj lapeit diya jayega
  81,2,Aur jab taarey bikhar jayenge
  81,3,Aur jab pahad chalaye jayenge
  81,4,Aur jab dus mahine ki hamila ountniyan (she-camels) apne haal par chod di jayengi
  81,5,Aur jab jungli jaanwar sameth kar ikhattey kar diye jayenge
  81,6,Aur jab samandar bhadka diye jayenge
  81,7,Aur jab jaane (Jismon se) jodh di jayengi
  81,8,Aur jab zinda gaadi hui(buried) ladki se pucha jayega
  81,9,ke woh kis kasoor mei mari gayi
  81,10,Aur jab aamal-naame(scrolls of deeds) kholey jayenge
  81,11,Aur jab aasman ka purda hata diya jayega
  81,12,Aur jab Jahannam dehkayi jayegi
  81,13,Aur jab Jannat qareeb le aayi jayegi
  81,14,Us waqt har shaks ko maloom ho jayega ke woh kya lekar aaya hai
  81,15,Pas nahin main kasam khata hoon
  81,16,Palatne aur chup janey wale taaron ki
  81,17,Aur Raat ki jabke woh ruksat hui
  81,18,Aur subah ki jabke usne saans liya
  81,19,Yeh fil waqea ek buzurg paigam-bar ka qaul(word) hai
  81,20,"Jo badi tawanai (might) rakhta hai, Arsh waley ke yahan buland martaba hai"
  81,21,"Wahan uska hukum mana jata hai, Woh ba-aitamad (trustworthy) hai"
  81,22,Aur (aey ehle Makkah) tumhara rafeeq(companion) majnoon(mad) nahin hai
  81,23,Usne us paigambar ko roshan ufaq (clear horizon) par dekha hai
  81,24,Aur woh gaib (ke is ilam ko logon tak pahunchane) ke maamle mei bakheel nahin hai
  81,25,Aur yeh kisi shaitan-e-mardood ka qaul nahin hai
  81,26,Phir tum log kidhar chaley ja rahey ho
  81,27,Yeh to saarey jahan walon ke liye ek naseehat hai
  81,28,Tum mein se har us shaks ke liye jo raah-e-raast par chalna chahta ho
  81,29,Aur tumharey chahney se kuch nahin hota jab tak Allah Rabb-ul-Aalameen na chahey
  82,1,Jab Aasman phat jayega
  82,2,Aur jab taarey bikhar jayengey
  82,3,Aur jab samandar phaad diye jayengey
  82,4,Aur jab qabrein khol di jayengi
  82,5,Us waqt har shaks ko uska agla pichla sab kiya dhara maloom ho jayega
  82,6,Aey insaan kis cheez ne tujhey apne uss Rubb-e-kareem ki taraf se dhoke mein daal diya
  82,7,"Jisne tujhey paida kiya, tujhey nek-suk se durust kiya(shaped you), tujhe mutanasib(well-proportioned) banaya"
  82,8,Aur jis surat mein chaha tujhko jodh kar tayyar kiya
  82,9,Hargiz nahin balke (asal baat yeh hai ke) tumlog jaza-o-saza ko jhutlate ho
  82,10,Halaanke tumpar nigraan muqarrar hain
  82,11,Aisey muazzaz kaatib
  82,12,Jo tumharey har fail(amal) ko jantey hain
  82,13,Yaqeenan neik log mazey mei hongey
  82,14,Aur beshak badkar log jahannam me jayenge
  82,15,Jaza ke din woh is mein daakhil hongey
  82,16,Aur us se hargiz gayab na ho sakengey
  82,17,Aur tum kya jaante ho ke woh jaza ka din kya hai
  82,18,Haan tumhein kya khabar ke woh jaza ka din kya hai
  82,19,"Yeh woh din hai jab kisi shaks ke liye kuch karna kisi ke bas mei na hoga, faisla us din bilkul Allah ke ikhtiyar mein hoga"
  83,1,Tabahi hai dandi maarne walon ke liye
  83,2,Jinka haal yeh hai ke jab logon se letey hai to pura pura letey hai
  83,3,Aur jab unko naap kar ya toal kar dete hai to unhein ghata dete hai
  83,4,Kya yeh log nahin samajhte ke ek badey din
  83,5,Yeh utha kar laaye jaaney waley hain
  83,6,Uss din jabke sab log Rabb-ul-Aalamin ke samney khadey hongey
  83,7,"Hargiz nahin, yaqeenan badkaaron ka naam-e- aamal qaid-khane ke daftar mei hai"
  83,8,Aur tumhey kya maloom ke woh qaid-khaney ka daftar kya hai
  83,9,Ek kitaab hai likhi hui
  83,10,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlane walon ke liye
  83,11,Jo roz-e-jaza ko jhutlatay hain
  83,12,Aur usey nahin jhutlata magar har woh shaks jo hadd se guzar janey wala bad-amal hai
  83,13,Usey jab hamari ayaat sunayi jaati hain to kehta hai yeh to agley waqton ki kahaniyan hai
  83,14,"Hargiz nahin, balke darasal in logon ke dilon par inke burey aamal ka zang(rust) chadh gaya hai"
  83,15,Hargiz nahin bil yaqeen us roz yeh apne Rubb ki deed(deedar) se mehroom rakhey jayenge
  83,16,Phir yeh jahannum mein jaa padenge
  83,17,Phir insey kaha jayega ke yeh wahi cheez hai jisey tum jhutlaya karte thay
  83,18,"Hargiz nahin, beshak neik aadmion ka naam-e-aamal buland paya logon ke daftar mein hai"
  83,19,Aur tumhein kya khabar ke kya hai woh buland paya logon ka daftar
  83,20,Ek likhi hui kitaab hai
  83,21,Jiski nigeh-daasht muqarrab farishtay karte hain
  83,22,Beshak neik log badey mazey mein hongey
  83,23,Unchi masnadon(couches) par baithay nazarey kar rahey hongey
  83,24,Unke chehron par tum khushhaali ki raunak mehsoos karogey
  83,25,Unko nafees tareen sarband sharaab pilayi jayegi jispar mushk ki mohar(seal) lagi hogi
  83,26,Jo log dusron par baazi le jana chahtey hon woh is cheez ko haasil karne mei baazi le jane ki koshish karein
  83,27,Us sharaab mei tasneem ki aamezish(mixture) hogi
  83,28,Yeh ek chasma hai jiske paani ke saath muqarrab log sharaab piyengey
  83,29,Mujrim log duniya mein imaan laane walon ka mazaak udate thay
  83,30,Jab unke paas se guzarte to aankhein maar maar kar unki taraf isharey karte thay
  83,31,Apne gharon ki taraf palat-tey to mazey letey huey palat-tey thay
  83,32,Aur jab unhein dekhte to kehte thay ke yeh behke huey log hain
  83,33,Halaanke woh un par nigran banakar nahin bhejey gaye thay
  83,34,Aaj imaan laane waley kuffar par hans rahay hai
  83,35,Masnadon par baithey huey unka haal dekh rahey hain
  83,36,Mil gaya na kafiron ko un harkaton ka sawab jo woh kiya karte thay
  84,1,Jab aasman phatt jayega
  84,2,Aur apne Rubb kay famaan ki tameel karega aur uske liye haq yahi hai (ke apne Rubb ka hukum maney)
  84,3,Aur jab zameen phaila di jayegi
  84,4,Aur jo kuch uske andar hai usey bahar phenk kar khaali ho jayegi
  84,5,Aur apne Rubb ke hukum ki tameel karegi aur uske liye haq yahi hai (kay uski tameel karey)
  84,6,Aey insaan tu kashaan kashaan apne Rubb ki taraf chala ja raha hai(striving unto your Lord) aur ussey milney wala hai
  84,7,Phir jiska naam-e-aamal uske seedhey haath mei diya gaya
  84,8,Ussey halka hisaab liya jayega
  84,9,Aur woh apne logon ki taraf khush khush paltega
  84,10,Raha woh shaks jiska naam-e-aamal us ki peeth ke pichey diya jayega
  84,11,To woh maut ko pukarega
  84,12,Aur bhadakti hui aag mei ja padega
  84,13,Woh apne ghar walon mein magan tha
  84,14,Usne samjha tha ke usey kabhi palatna nahin hai
  84,15,"Palatna kaise na tha, uska Rubb uske kartoot dekh raha tha"
  84,16,Pas nahin mai kasam khata hon shafaq(twilight) ki
  84,17,Aur raat ki aur jo kuch woh sameith leti hai
  84,18,Aur chaand ki jabke woh maah-e-kaamil (full) ho jata hai
  84,19,Tumko zaroor darja ba darja ek haalat se dusri halat ki taraf guzarte chalay jana hai
  84,20,Phir in logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke yeh imaan nahin laatey
  84,21,Aur jab Quran inke samney pada jata hai to sajda nahin karte
  84,22,Balke yeh munkireen to ulta jhutlatay hain
  84,23,Halaanke jo kuch yeh (apne naam-e-aamal mein) jama kar rahey hain Allah usey khoob janta hai
  84,24,Lihaza inko dardnaak azaab ki basharat dedo
  84,25,Albatta jo log imaan le aaye hain aur jinho ne neik aamal kiye hain unke liye kabhi khatam na honay wala ajar hai
  85,1,Kasam hai mazboot qalon waley (impregnable castles )aasman ki
  85,2,Aur us din ki jiska wada kiya gaya hai
  85,3,Aur dekhnay walay ki aur dekhi janey wali cheez ki
  85,4,kay maarey gaye gaddey(pit) waley
  85,5,"uss gaddey(pit) waley] jis mei khoob bhadakte huey indhan ki aag thi"
  85,6,jabke woh us gaddey ke kinare par baithay huey thay
  85,7,Aur jo kuch woh imaan laney walon ke saath kar rahey thay usey dekh rahey thay
  85,8,Aur un ehley imaan se unki dushmani iske siwa kisi wajah se na thi ke woh us khuda par imaan le aaye thay jo zabardast aur apni zaat mei aap mahmood(praiseworthy) hai
  85,9,"Jo aasmano aur zameen ki sultanat ka maalik hai, aur woh khuda sab kuch dekh raha hai"
  85,10,"Jin logon ne momin mardon aur auraton par zulm o sitam toda aur phir ussey taib na huey, yaqeenan unke liye jahannum ka azaab hai aur unke liye jalaye janey ki saza hai"
  85,11,"Jo log imaan laaye aur jinho ne neik amal kiye yaqeenan unke liye jannat ke baagh hain jinke nichey nehrein behti hongi, yeh hai badi kamyabi"
  85,12,Dar haqeeqat tumharey Rubb ki pakad badi sakht hai
  85,13,Wahi pehli baar paida karta hai aur wahi dobara paida karega
  85,14,"Aur woh bakshne wala hai, mohabbat karne wala hai"
  85,15,"Arsh ka maalik hai, buzurg-o-bartar hai"
  85,16,Aur jo kuch chahey kar daalney wala hai
  85,17,Kya tumhey lashkaron ki khabar pahunchi hai
  85,18,Firoun aur samood (ke lashkaron) ki
  85,19,Magar jinho ne kufr kiya hai woh jhutlaney mein lagey huey hain
  85,20,Halaanke Allah ne unko gherey mein le rakha hai
  85,21,(unke jhutlaney se iss quran ka kuch nahin bigadta) balkey yeh quran buland paya hai
  85,22,Us loah mei (naqsh hai) jo mehfooz hai
  86,1,Kasam hai aasmaan ki aur raat ko namudaar honay wale ki
  86,2,Aur tum kya jaano kay woh raat ko namudaar honay wala kya hai
  86,3,Chamakta hua tara
  86,4,koi jaan aisi nahin hai jiske upar koi nigehbaan na ho
  86,5,Phir zara Insan yahi dekh le ke woh kis cheez se paida kiya gaya hai
  86,6,Ek uchalne wale pani se paida kiya gaya hai
  86,7,Jo peet aur seeney ki haddiyon kay darmiyan se nikalta hai
  86,8,Yaqeenan woh (khaliq) usey dobara paida karne par qadir hai
  86,9,Jis roz poshida asraar ki jaanch padtal hogi
  86,10,Us waqt Insan ke paas na khud apna koi zoar hoga aur na koi uski madad karne wala hoga
  86,11,Kasam hai baarish barsane waley aasman ki
  86,12,Aur (nabataat ugte waqt) phatt jane wali zameen ki
  86,13,Yeh ek jachi-tuli baat hai
  86,14,Hasi mazak nahin hai
  86,15,yeh log kuch chalein chal rahe hain
  86,16,Aur mai bhi ek chaal chal raha hoon
  86,17,"Pas chodh do aey nabi, in kafiron ko ek zara ki zara in ke haal par chod do"
  87,1,(Aey nabi) Apne Rubb-e-bartar kay naam ki tasbeeh karo
  87,2,Jisne paida kiya aur tanasub qayam kiya (then proportioned it)
  87,3,Jisne taqdeer banayi phir raah dikhayi
  87,4,Jisne nabataat(pasture) ugayi
  87,5,Phir unko siyah kuda karkat bana diya
  87,6,Hum tumhey padhwa dengey phir tum nahin bhuloge
  87,7,Siwaye uske jo Allah chahey.Woh zahir ko bhi jaanta hai aur jo kuch posheeda(hidden) hai usko bhi
  87,8,Aur hum tumhein aasaan tarikey ki sahoolat dete hain
  87,9,lihaza tum naseehat karo agar naseehat nafey(faiydamand) ho
  87,10,Jo shaks darta hai wo naseehat qabool karlega
  87,11,Aur ussey guraiz karega woh intehayi bad-bakht
  87,12,Jo badi aag mei jayega
  87,13,phir na usmein marega aur na jiyega
  87,14,Falah paa gaya woh jisne pakizgi ikhtiyar ki
  87,15,Aur apne Rubb ka naam yaad kiya phir namaz padhi
  87,16,Magar tumlog duniya ki zindagi ko tarjeeh detay ho
  87,17,halaanke aakhirat behtar hai aur baqi rehne wali hai
  87,18,Yahi baat pehle aaey huey saheefon(scriptures) mei bhi kahi gayi thi
  87,19,Ibrahim aur Moosa ke saheefon mein
  88,1,Kya tumhein us chaa janey wali aafat ki khabar pahunchi hai
  88,2,Kuch chehrey us roz khauff zada hongey
  88,3,Sakht mashakkat kar rahe hongey
  88,4,"Thakey jatey hongey, shadeed aag mei jhulas rahe hongey"
  88,5,khaultey(boiling) huey chashmey(spring) ka paani unhei peene ko diya jaeyga
  88,6,khar-dar(kaante-daar) sukhi ghaans ke siwa koi khana unke liye na hoga
  88,7,Jo na mota karey na bhook mitaye
  88,8,kuch chehrey us roz ba-raunak hongey
  88,9,Apne kar-guzari par khush hongey
  88,10,Aali muqaam jannat mein hongey
  88,11,koi behuda baat wahan na sunengey
  88,12,Usmein chasmey rawan hongey
  88,13,Uske andar unchi masnadein hongi
  88,14,Sagar rakhey huey hongey
  88,15,gaon takiyon(cushions arrayed) ke qatarein lagi hongi
  88,16,Aur nafees farsh bichey huey hongey
  88,17,(yeh log nahin mantey) to kya yeh unton ko nahin dekhtey ke kaisey banaye gaye
  88,18,Asman ko nahin dekhte ke kaise uthaya gaya
  88,19,Pahadon ko nahin dekhtey ke kaisey jamaye gaye
  88,20,Aur zameen ko nahin dekhtey ke kaisey bichayi gayi
  88,21,"Acha to ( aey nabi) nasihat kiye jao, tum bas nasihat hi karne wale ho"
  88,22,kuch inpar jabr karne wale nahin ho
  88,23,Albatta jo shaks mooh modega aur inkar karega
  88,24,To Allah usko bhaari saza dega
  88,25,In logon ko palatna hamari taraf hi hai
  88,26,Phir inka hisab lena hamare hi zimmey hai
  89,1,Kasam hai fajr ki
  89,2,Aur dus raaton ki
  89,3,Aur jufft(even) aur taaq(odd) ki
  89,4,Aur Raat ki jabke woh ruksat ho rahi ho
  89,5,kya ismein kisi sahib-e-aqal ke liye koi kasam hai
  89,6,Tumne dekha nahin ke tumhare Rubb ne kya bartao kiya
  89,7,Unchey sutuno waley Aad-e-iram kay saath
  89,8,Jinke manind koi qaum duniya kay mulkon mein paida nahin ki gayi thi
  89,9,Aur Samood ke saath jinhon ne wadi mei chattane tarashi thi
  89,10,Aur mekhon waley Firoun kay saath
  89,11,Yeh woh log (thay) jinhone duniya kay mulkon mein badi sarkashi ki thi
  89,12,Aur inmein bahut fasaad failaya tha
  89,13,Aakhir-e-kaar tumhare Rubb ne inpar azaab ka koda barsa diya
  89,14,Haqeeqat yeh hai kay tumhara Rubb ghaath(watchful) lagaye huey hai
  89,15,Magar Insan ka haal yeh hai kay uska Rubb jab usko aazmaish mein daalta hai aur usey izzat aur niyamat deta hai to woh kehta hai kay mere Rubb ne mujhey izzatdar bana diya
  89,16,Aur jab woh usko azmaish mein daalta hai aur uska rizq uspar tangg kar deta hai to woh kehta hai mere Rubb ne mujhey zaleel kar diya
  89,17,"Hargiz nahin, balke tum yateem se izzat ka sulook nahin kartey"
  89,18,Aur miskeen ko khana khilane par ek dusrey ko nahin uksatey
  89,19,Aur Miras(inheritance) ka sara maal sameith kar kha jatey ho
  89,20,Aur maal ki muhabbat mei buri tarah giraftar ho
  89,21,Hargiz nahin jab zameen pai dar pai qoot qoot kar regzaar bana di jayegi
  89,22,Aur tumahra Rubb jalwa farma hoga is haal mei kay farishtey saff dar saff khade hongey
  89,23,"Aur jahannum us roz samnay le aayi jaeygi, us din Insan ko samajh ayegi aur us waqt us ke samajhne ka kya hasil"
  89,24,Woh kahega ke kaash maine apni is zindagi ke liye kuch peshgi saman kiya hota
  89,25,Phir us din Allah jo azaab dega waisa azaab dene wala koi nahin
  89,26,Aur Allah jaisa bandhega waisa bandhne wala koi nahin
  89,27,(Dusri taraf irshad hoga) Aey nafsey mutmain(reassured soul/pious)
  89,28,Chal apne Rubb ki taraf is haal mein ke tu (apne anjam-e-neik se) khush (Aur apne Rubb kay nazdeek) pasandida hai
  89,29,Shamil ho ja mere (neik) bandon mein
  89,30,Aur dakhil hoja meri jannat mein
  90,1,Nahin mai kasam khata hoon is shehar(city) ki
  90,2,Aur haal yeh hai ke (Aey nabi) is shehar mein tumko halal kar liya gaya hai
  90,3,Aur kasam khata hoon baap(Adam) ki aur us aulad ki jo ussey paida hui
  90,4,Dar haqeeqat humne Insan ko mushakkat mein paida kiya hai
  90,5,Kya usne yeh samajh rakhha hai kay uspar koi qaabu na paa sakega
  90,6,Kehta hai ke maine dhairon maal udaa diya
  90,7,Kya woh samajhta hai kay kisi ne usko nahin dekha
  90,8,Kya humne usey do aankhein
  90,9,Aur ek zubaan aur do honth nahin diye
  90,10,Aur dono numayan raste usey (nahin) dikha diye
  90,11,Magar usne dushwar guzar ghati(steep) se guzarne ki himmat na ki
  90,12,Aur tum kya jaano kay kya hai woh dushwar guzar ghaati
  90,13,Kisi gardan ko gulami se chudana
  90,14,Ya faake ke din
  90,15,kisi qareebi yateem
  90,16,Ya khaak nasheen miskeen ko khana khilana
  90,17,Phir (iske saath yeh kay) aadmi un logon mein shamil ho jo imaan laye aur jinhon ne ek dusrey ko sabr aur (khalq-e-khuda par) raham ki talqeen ki
  90,18,Yeh log hain dayein baazu(right hand) waley
  90,19,Aur jinhon ne hamari aayat ko mann-ney se inkar kiya woh bayen bazu(left hand) waley hain
  90,20,Un par aag chaayi hui hogi
  91,1,Suraj aur uski dhoop ki kasam
  91,2,Aur Chand ki kasam jabke wo uske pichey aata hai
  91,3,Aur din ki kasam jabke woh (Suraj ko) numaya kar deta hai
  91,4,Aur raat ki kasam jabke woh (suraj ko) dhank leti hai
  91,5,Aur aasman ki aur us zaat ki kasam jisne usey qayam kiya
  91,6,Aur zameen ki aur us zaat ki kasam jisne usey bichaya
  91,7,Aur nafs-e-Insani ki aur us zaat ki kasam jisne usey hamwar kiya
  91,8,Phir uski badi aur uski parhezgari uss par ilham kar di
  91,9,Yaqeenan falah pa gaya woh jisne nafs ka tazkiya kiya
  91,10,Aur na-murad hua woh jisne usko daba diya
  91,11,Samood ne apni sarkashi ki bina par jhutlaya
  91,12,Jab us qaum ka sab se zyada shaqi (Badnaseeb) aadmi biphar kar utha
  91,13,To Allah ke Rasool ne un logon se kaha ke khabardar Allah ki ountni (she-camel) ko (haath na lagana) aur uske paani peene (mein maane na hona)
  91,14,Magar unhon ne uski baat ko jhuta qarar diya aur ountni ko maar dala. Aakhir-e-kaar unke gunah ke padash mein unke Rubb ne unpar aisi aafat toodi ke ek saath sab ko paywand-e-khaaq kar diya
  91,15,Aur usey (apne is fail kay) kisi burey natije ka koi khauf(darr) nahin hai
  92,1,Kasam hai raat ki jabke woh chaa jaaye
  92,2,Aur din ki jabke woh roshan ho
  92,3,Aur us zaat ki jisne nar(male) aur maada(female) ko paida kiya
  92,4,Dar haqeeqat tum logon ki koshishein mukhtalif qism ki hai
  92,5,To jisne (rah e khuda mein) maal diya aur (khuda ki nafarmani se) parhez kiya
  92,6,Aur bhalayi ko sach mana
  92,7,Usko hum aasan raastey kay liye sahulat denge
  92,8,Aur jisne bukhl(kanjoosi) kiya aur (apney khuda se) be niyazi(self-sufficient/independent) barti
  92,9,aur bhalayi ko jhutlaya
  92,10,Usko hum sakht rastey kay liye sahulat dengey
  92,11,Aur uska maal aakhir uske kis kaam aayega jabke woh halaq ho jaye
  92,12,Beshak rasta batana hamare zimmey hai
  92,13,aur dar haqeeqat aakhirat aur duniya dono kay hum hi malik hai
  92,14,Pas maine tumko khabardar kar diya hai bhadakti hui aag se
  92,15,Usmein nahin jhulsega magar woh intihayi badbakth
  92,16,jisne jhutlaya aur mooh phera
  92,17,Aur usse door rakkha jayega woh nihayat parhezgaar
  92,18,Jo paakiza honay ki khatir apna maal deta hai
  92,19,Uspar kisi ka koi ehsan nahin hai jiska badla usey dena ho
  92,20,Woh to sirf apne Rubb-e-bartrar ki raza joii ke liye yeh kaam karta hai
  92,21,Aur zaroor woh (us se) khush hoga
  93,1,Kasam hai rozey roshan ki
  93,2,Aur raat ki jabke woh sukoon ke saath taari ho jaye
  93,3,(Aey nabi) tumharey Rubb ne tumko hargiz nahin chodha aur na woh naraaz hua
  93,4,Aur yaqeenan tumhare liya baad ka daur pehle daur se behtar hai
  93,5,Aur anqareeb tumhra Rubb tumko itna dega ke tum khush ho jaogey
  93,6,Kya usne tumko yateem nahin paya aur phir thikana faraham kiya
  93,7,Aur tumhey nawaqif-e-raah paya aur phir hidayat bakshi
  93,8,Aur tumhein nadaar(in want) paya aur phir maldar kar diya
  93,9,Lihaza yateem par sakhti na karo
  93,10,Aur saayil(maangne waley) ko na jhidko
  93,11,Aur apne Rubb ki niyamt ka izhar karo
  94,1,(Aey Nabi) kya humne tumhara seena tumhare liye khol nahin diya
  94,2,Aur tumpar se woh bhari bojh utar diya
  94,3,Jo tumhari qamar todhe daal raha tha
  94,4,Aur tumhare khatir tumharey zikr ka awazah buland kar diya
  94,5,Pas haqeeqat yeh hai kay tangi kay saat farakhi bhi hai
  94,6,Beshak tangi kay saath farakhi bhi hai
  94,7,Lihaza jab tum faarig ho to Ibadat ki mushakkat mei lag jao
  94,8,Aur apne Rubb ki taraf raagib ho
  95,1,Kasam hai Injir(fig) ki aur Zaitun ki
  95,2,Aur Tur-e-sina (Mount Sinai)
  95,3,Aur is pur-aman shehar (Makkah) ki
  95,4,Humne Insan ko behtarin saakht par paida kiya
  95,5,Phir usey ulta pher kar humne sab neechon se neech kar diya
  95,6,Siwaye un logon ke jo iman laye aur neik amal karte rahey kay unke liye kabhi khatam na hone wala ajar hai
  95,7,Pas (aey nabi) iske baad kaun jaza o saza ke maamle mei tumko jhutla sakta hai
  95,8,Kya Allah sab hakimon se bada hakim nahin hai
  96,1,Padho (Aey Nabi) apne Rubb ke naam ke saath Jisne paida kiya
  96,2,Jamey huey khoon ke ek lothdey se Insan ki takhliq ki
  96,3,Padho aur tumhara Rubb bada kareem hai
  96,4,jisne qalam ke zariya se ilm sikhaya
  96,5,Insan ko woh ilm diya jisey woh na jaanta tha
  96,6,"Hargiz nahin, Insan sarkahshi karta hai"
  96,7,Is bina par ke woh apne aap ko be niyaz dekhta hai
  96,8,(halaanke) palatna yaqeenan tere Rubb hi ki taraf hai
  96,9,Tumne dekha us shaks ko
  96,10,Jo ek banday ko mana karta hai jabke woh namaz padta ho
  96,11,Tumhara kya khayal hai agar (woh banda) raah e raast par ho
  96,12,ya parhezgari ki talqeen karta ho
  96,13,Tumhara kya khayal hai agar (yeh mana karne wala shakhs haqq ko) jhutlata aur mooh moadta ho
  96,14,Kya woh nahin jaanta ke Allah dekh raha hai
  96,15,Hargiz nahin agar woh baaz na aaya to hum uski peshani ke baal pakad kar usey khinchey ge
  96,16,Us peshani ko jo jhooti aur sakth khatakaar hai
  96,17,Woh bulaley apne haamiyon ki toli ko
  96,18,Hum bhi azaab ke farishton ko bula lengey
  96,19,"Hargiz nahin, uski baat na mano aur sajda karo aur (apne Rubb ka) qurb hasil karo"
  97,1,Humne is (Quran) ko shab-e-qadr mei nazil kiya hai
  97,2,Aur tum kya jano kay shab-e-qadr kya hai
  97,3,Shab-e-qadr hazar mahino se zyada behtar hai
  97,4,Farishtey aur rooh(Jibrael) us mein apne Rubb ke izn(permission) se har hukm le kar utarte hai
  97,5,Woh raat sarasar salamati hai tulu e fajr tak
  98,1,Ehle kitab aur Mushrikin mein se jo log kafir thay (woh apne kufr se) baaz aane walay na thay jab tak ke unke paas dalil e roshan na aa jaye
  98,2,(Yani) Allah ke taraf se ek Rasool jo paak sahife padh kar sunaye
  98,3,Jin mein bilkul raast aur durust tehrirein likhi hui ho
  98,4,Pehle jin logon ko kitab di gayi thi unmei tafarqa barpa(split/divide) nahin hua magar is ke baad ke un ke paas (raahe rast ka) bayan e wazeh aa chuka tha
  98,5,"Aur unko iske siwa koi hukum nahin diya gaya tha ke Allah ke bandagi karein apne deen ko uske liye khalis karke. Bilkul yaksu ho kar, Aur namaz qayam karein aur zakat de yahi nihayat sahih-o-durust deen hai"
  98,6,"Ehle kitaab aur mushrikin mein se jin logon ne kufr kiya hai woh yaqeenan jahannam ki aag mein jayenge aur hamesha us mein rahenge, yeh log badh-tareen e khalayek(creation) hain"
  98,7,Jo log iman le aaye aur jinhon nay neik amal kiye woh yaqeenan behtareen-e-khalayeq hai
  98,8,Unki jaza unke Rubb ke yahan dayimi(eternal) qayam ki jannatein hain jinke nichey nehrein beh rahi hongi. Woh unmein hamesha hamesh rahenge. Allah unse razi hua aur woh Allah se razi huey. Yeh kuch hai us shaks ke liye jisne apne Rubb ka khauf kiya ho
  99,1,Jab zameen apni puri shiddat kay saath hila daali jayegi
  99,2,Aur zameen apne andar kay sarey bojh nikal kar bahar daal degi
  99,3,Aur Insan kahega ke yeh isko kya ho raha hai
  99,4,Us roz woh apne (upar guzre huey) halaat bayan karegi
  99,5,Kyunke tere Rubb ne usey (aisa karne ka) hukm diya hoga
  99,6,Us roz log mutafarrik halat mein paltenge taakay unke aamal unko dikhaey jayein
  99,7,Phir jisne zarra barabar neki ki hogi woh usko dekh lega
  99,8,Aur jisne zarra barabar badi ki hogi woh usko dekh lega
  100,1,Kasam hai un (ghodon) ki jo phunkare marte hue dhaudte hai
  100,2,Phir (apne tapon se) chingariyan jhaadte hain
  100,3,Phir subah sawere chapa marte hain
  100,4,Phir is mauke par gard o gubar udatey hai
  100,5,Phir isi halat mei kisi majmey ke andar ja ghustey hai
  100,6,Haqiqat yeh hai ke Insan apne Rubb ka bada nashukra hai
  100,7,Aur woh khud is par gawah hai
  100,8,Aur woh maal-o-daulat ki muhabbat mei buri tarah mubtala hai
  100,9,To kya woh us waqt ko nahin janta jab qabron mein jo kuch (madfun) hai usey nikal liya jayega
  100,10,Aur seeno mein jo kuch (makhfi) hai usey baramad karke uski jaanch padtal ki jayegi
  100,11,Yaqeenan unka Rubb us roz unse khoob bakhabar hoga
  101,1,Azeem hadisa
  101,2,Kya hai woh azeem hadisa
  101,3,Tum kya jano ke woh azeem hadisa kya hai
  101,4,woh din jab log bhikre huey parwano ki tarah
  101,5,Aur pahad rang bi rangi dhunki hui oon ke tarah hongey
  101,6,Phir jiske palade bhari hongey
  101,7,Woh dil pasand aish mei hoga
  101,8,Aur jis kay palade halke hongey
  101,9,Uski jaye qarar gehri khayi hogi
  101,10,Aur tumhein kya khabar kay woh kya cheez hai
  101,11,Bhadakti hui Aag
  102,1,Tum logon ko zyada se zyada aur ek dusre se badh kar duniya hasil karne ki dhun ne gaflat mei daal rakha hai
  102,2,Yahan tak ke (isi fikr mei) tum lab-e-gaur tak pahunch jatey ho
  102,3,"Hargiz nahin, ankareeb tumko maloom ho jayega"
  102,4,"phir (sunlo kay) hargiz nahin, ankarib tumko maloom ho jayega"
  102,5,Hargiz nahin agar tum yaqeeni ilm ki haisiyat se (is rawish ke anjam ko) jantey hotey (to tumhara yeh tarze amal na hota)
  102,6,Tum dozakh dekh kar rahogey
  102,7,Phir (sun lo ke) tum bilkul yaqeen kay saath usey dekh logey
  102,8,Phir zaroor us roz tum se in neyamaton kay barey mein jawab talabi ki jayegi
  103,1,Zamane ki qasam
  103,2,Insan dar haqeeqat badey khasarey(nuksaan) mein hai
  103,3,Siwaye un logon ke jo iman laye aur neik aamal karte rahe aur ek dusrey ko haqq ki nasihat aur sabr ki talqeen karte rahe
  104,1,Tabahi hai har us shaks ke liye jo (moonh dar moonh) logon par taan aur (peeth peechey) buraiyan karne ka khugar hai
  104,2,Jisne maal jama kiya aur usey gin gin kar rakkha
  104,3,Woh samajhta hai ke us ka maal hamesha uske paas rahega
  104,4,"Hargiz nahin, woh shaks to chakna-chur kar dene wali jagah mein phenk diya jayega"
  104,5,Aur tum kya jano ke kya hai woh chakna-chur kar dene wali jagah
  104,6,Allah ki aag khoob bhadkayi hui
  104,7,Jo dilon tak pahunchey gi
  104,8,Woh un par dhaank kar bandh kar di jayegi
  104,9,(Is halat mei ke woh) unchey unchey sutuno mei (ghirey huey hongey)
  105,1,Tumne dekha nahin ke tumhare Rubb ne haathi walon ke saath kya kiya
  105,2,Kya usne unki tadbir ko akarat nahin kar diya
  105,3,Aur un par parindo ke jhund ke jhund bhej diye
  105,4,Jo un par pakey huey mitti ke patthar phenk rahey thay
  105,5,Phir un ka yeh haal kar diya jaise janwaron ka khaya hua bhoosa
  106,1,Chunke Quresh manoos huey
  106,2,(yani) Jaadey(winter) aur garmi ke safaron se manoos
  106,3,Lihaza un ko chahiye ke is ghar ke Rubb ki ibadat karein
  106,4,Jisne unhein bhook se bacha kar khane ko diya aur khauf se bacha kar aman ata kiya
  107,1,Tum ne dekha us shaks ko jo aakhirat ki jaza va saza ko jhutlata hai
  107,2,Wahi to hai jo yateem ko dhakkey deta hai
  107,3,Aur miskeen ka khana dene par nahin uksata
  107,4,Phir tabahi hai un namaz padhne walon ke liye
  107,5,Jo apni namaz se gaflat barat-tey hain
  107,6,Jo riya-kaari(dikhawa) karte hai
  107,7,Aur maamuli zarurat ki cheezen (logon ko) dene se gurez karte hai
  108,1,(Aey Nabi ) Hum ne tumhein kausar ata kar diya
  108,2,Pas tum apne Rubb hi ke liye namaz padho aur qurbani karo
  108,3,Tumhara dushman hi jadh-kata hai
  109,1,Kehdo ke aey kafiron
  109,2,Main unki ibadat nahin karta jinki ibadat tum karte ho
  109,3,Aur na tum uski ibadat karne wale ho jiski ibadat mai karta hoon
  109,4,Aur na mai unki ibadat karne wala hoon jinki ibadat tum ne ki hai
  109,5,Aur na tum uski ibadat karne waley ho jiski ibadat main karta hoon
  109,6,Tumhare liye tumhara deen hai aur mere liye mera deen
  110,1,Jab Allah ki madad aa jaye aur fatah naseeb ho jaye
  110,2,Aur (aey Nabi s.a.s) tum dekh lo ke log fauj dar fauj Allah ke deen mein dakhil ho rahey hain
  110,3,To apne Rubb ki hamd ke saath uski tasbeeh karo Aur us se magfirat ki duaa maango. Beshak woh bada tauba qabool karne wala hai
  111,1,Toot gaye Abu Lahab ke haath aur na-murad ho gaya woh
  111,2,Uska maal aur jo kuch us ne kamaya woh uske kisi kaam na aaya
  111,3,Zaroor woh shola zan Aag mei dala jayega
  111,4,Aur (us ke saath) us ki joru(wife) bhi lagai bujhai karne wali
  111,5,Us ki gardan(neck) mein moonj ki rassi hogi
  112,1,"Kaho woh Allah hai, Yakta"
  112,2,Allah sab se bay-niyaz hai aur sab us kay mohtaj hain
  112,3,Na uski koi aulad hai aur na woh kisi ki aulad
  112,4,Aur koi uska humsar nahin hai
  113,1,Kaho main panaah maangta hoon subah ke Rubb ki
  113,2,Har us cheez ke shar se jo usne paida ki hai
  113,3,Aur raat ki tareeki ke sharr se jab ke woh chaa jaye
  113,4,Aur girhon mein phoonkne walon (ya waliyon) ke sharr se
  113,5,Aur hasid(envies) ke sharr se jab ke woh hasad(envy) karey
  114,1,"Kaho, main panah maangta hoon insano ke Rubb"
  114,2,Insano ke badshah
  114,3,Insano ke hakiki maabood ki
  114,4,us waswasa dalne wale ke shar se jo baar baar palat kar aata hai
  114,5,Jo logon ke dilon mei waswasey daalta hai
  114,6,khwah woh jinno mein se ho ya Insano mein se